Ice time lapse analysis

Getting started.

Let’s load up a bunch of photos

library(EBImage)
pics<-dir(pattern=".JPG")  ## Load a directory of images
head(pics)
## [1] "G0110614.JPG" "G0110615.JPG" "G0110616.JPG" "G0110617.JPG"
## [5] "G0110618.JPG" "G0110619.JPG"
p1<-readImage(pics[5]) ## Read a picture 
fp<-flip(p1) ### Rotate
